{"tid":2141024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本防衛大臣河野太郎據報有意角逐下任首相","createTime":"2020-08-05T11:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T12:41:19.000Z","uid":75656,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91a367019ba177c3574c43bfbebfe58a8b720a09","tid":2141024,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"日本防衛大臣河野太郎接受即將出版的雜誌訪問，透露有意角逐下任首相。<br />\n<br />\n被問到負責過外交及防衛方面，接下來會是哪裡，河野太郎說，想進入首相官邸，表明會盡最大努力爭取成為下任首相。<br />\n<br />\n對於執政自民黨內有人對他有不同意見，河野說，期望以他個人表現作判斷，又提到若果當選，希望停用核能發電，並改革養老金等社保制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541967-20200805.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541967-20200805.htm&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=35c61f56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541967-20200805.htm&h=c0c98acf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541967-20200805.htm</a>"},{"pid":"12d5cf5e842e978a0bf60dd97c4cb753371497b9","tid":2141024,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91a367019ba177c3574c43bfbebfe58a8b720a09","tid":2141024,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"日本防衛大臣河野太郎接受即將出版的雜誌訪問，透露有意角逐下任首相。<br />\n<br />\n被問到負責過外交及防衛方面，接下來會是哪裡，河野太郎說，想進入首相官邸，表明會盡最大努力爭取成為下任首相。<br />\n<br />\n對於執政自民黨內有人對他有不同意見，河野說，期望以他個人表現作判斷，又提到若果當選，希望停用核能發電，並改革養老金等社保制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541967-20200805.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541967-20200805.htm&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=35c61f56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541967-20200805.htm&h=c0c98acf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541967-2